#

Avocado Burger

25 min
$12.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

Quick MealComfort Food

Description

A delicious and fulfilling burger topped with creamy avocado and fresh vegetables, perfect for a quick meal!

Ingredients

  • ground beef (or plant-based alternative): 1 lb
  • burger buns: 4
  • avocado: 2
  • lettuce leaves: 4
  • tomato slices: 1
  • cheddar cheese (optional): 4 slices
  • mayonnaise: 4 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • onion powder: 1 tsp
